schoorbs (1.0a5) unstable; urgency=low

  * Removed grab_globals.php, which extracted all _GET, _POST and _COOKIE variables as global variables
  * Rewritten edit_entry.php and edit_entry_handler.php to work without grab_globals.php
  * Removed automated mails when booking a room
  * Added logging system, at the moment only syslog is available as a backend
  * Supporting Smarty 2.6.19
  * Official(tested) Support now for 
  * Ubuntu 7.10 "Gutsy Gibbon"
  * Ubuntu 7.04 "Feisty Fawn"
  * Debian 4.0 "Etch"

 -- Uwe L. Korn <packaging@xhochy.com>  Sun, 17 Feb 2008 15:09:16 +0100

